Creating the Visual , YoY and Month name 12

Create Approved Cases Months Chart.

-          Double click on the â€œLine and Stacked column Chart" On the visualization bar.

-          Chart visual will display on the report.

-          Drag and drop the "Month" column from the Date table

-    Drag and drop the "quarter" column from the date table

-          Drag and drop Approved Cases column from the H-1B Visas table

-          Drag and drop the YOY% column from H-1B Visa table

-          Click Format, General  on Y axis  input -103 width -583 Height - 264

       click on Legend Name, on color, Black, text size 9, turn title off

-          Click on X Axis, color= Black, text size 9, title =off

-          Background color, mid grey #ccccccc

-          Click Data colors, YoY= Sky blue- #118DFF,default color = light Brown- #a93600

-          Click Data label, color = black, text size 9, put customize series on, then chose Approved Cases, color = White, text size 9, font, segoe UI

-          Click Shape- shade on-stroke =3, Show Maker-On- Marker shade . Marker size= 5 Color- White

-          Turn title on, write Approved Cases | YOY by Month in the box Font color = White, background color =Dark brown- # 6d5900, Center, text size 14

-          Click Background on- Color-grey #ccccccc
